bropd package

Version: 1.2 2014/10/14

by Benjamin Tatlock

The bropd package simplifies the process of writing differential operators and
brackets in LaTeX. The commands facilitate the easy manipulation of equations
involving brackets and allow partial differentials to be expressed in
alternate forms.


The "bropd" package is copyright 2012 by Benjamin Tatlock

It comprises this README file, as well as files
bropd.dtx
bropd.pdf
bropd.sty

Run LaTeX on the documented source file bropd.dtx to install the package and
generate the accompanying documentation.

